    "In detail, while position embedding layers encoding the coordinate as f p, and linear layers encoding the size f q and color f c, we have 3D Scene EncoderWe use EPCL [10] as our pre-trained 3D Scene Encoder which directly leverage the frozen CLIP [15] transformer as the encoder for point cloud tasks.",
